    "# Stage 4 — Walk-Forward Robustness\n",
    "\n",
    "6-month rolling window across the full dataset: train on past 6 months, test on next 1 month, advance one month, repeat.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Acceptance criterion:** ≥ 80% of test months must produce PF > 1.0.\n",
    "\n",
    "Detects regime-overfit that a static IS/OOS split cannot catch."
   ]
